#note just a huge letdown to go all this way to play this tournament, work hard to get to the top few tables, and then put up such a miserable effort. Undoubtedly one of my worst games since coming back from china. what happened? I just got too tired. I tried hard not to let it influence my next game but I was definitely down and low on energy for my next matchup against odette. I think this was my worst game of the tournament. Lesson is that I need to find a way to sustain energy levels late in the afternoon. More coffee? No coffee? More sleep? I thought I was doing ok in the latter regard, but maybe I need to force myself to go to bed earlier.
